title: Ganbare! Lulu Lolo (TINY★TWIN★BEARS)
synopsis: The new anime centers around the daily life of two twin bear sisters: the orange-colored Lulu and the yellow-colored Lolo. The two take on new jobs and despite the occasional failure and tears, give their best efforts.
related_anime: ['Kuma no Gakkou: Jackie to Katie', 'Ganbare! Lulu Lolo 2nd Season']
